You can choose to restrict yourself for specific Game Variants. You can choose the blinds of the tables from which you want to restrict yourself and the duration. Once the restriction is set, you will not be able to play on those blinds until the set number of hours or days.
Note: Once the restriction limits are set, you can alter them as:
Blinds can be lowered from the set limit. They cannot be increased further during the restriction period.
Duration can be increased from the set limit. It cannot be decreased during the restriction period.
Cannot be greater than Daily or Weekly limit
Cannot be less than Daily limit or Per transaction limit
Day is treated as 12:00:00 AM - 11:59:59 PM.Week is treated as Sunday - Saturday.
Once the deposit limit (Amount or Count)is set, you cannot increase the limit (Amount or Count) for 7 days, except for reducing the limits.
When you set your deposit limit, any deposit you have made in the passed days of that week will count towards your new deposit limit.

Example: 8L now you cannot deposit more than Rs. 6L and you deposited Rs 5L and changed the deposit limit to Rs. 8 L now you cannot deposit more than Rs 3L till the week ends. Rs. 8L limit will be available from next week.

Set custom Self-Exclusion limit to block yourself from playing any game on Adda52 Poker. Once set, the App will restrict you from playing any Poker variant across the App, in addition, no cash deposits will be allowed during the period of time selected by you
You will however be allowed to log in the App, make withdrawals requests as applicable.
If you are pre-registered for any SnG or Cash tournaments, you will be unregistered from the same and the amount will be credited back to your Deposit wallet.
Running Cash games, SNG tournaments that you are registered for/playing remain unaffected by these set limits.
Note: Once the time period is set, you cannot change it back during that window.
Set custom Sit n Go (SnG) Table limits based on the Buy-in price to participate in a SNG Tournament.
Once set, the App will restrict you from playing SnG Tourneys where the Buy-in fee is more than the limit set.
You can choose the “Play-All” option If you want access to all Tournaments on the App
I Don’t Want To Play Any SnG
If you are pre-registered for any SnG that are higher than the Buy-in limit opted for, you will be unregistered from the same and the amount will be credited back to your Deposit wallet.
Running SnG tournaments that you are registered for remain unaffected by these set limits.
Note: Once Table limit is set, you cannot change them for 7 days, except for reducing the limits.
Set custom Tournament limits based on the Buy-in price to participate in a Tournament.
Once set, the app will restrict you from playing Poker Tourneys on any table where the Buy-in fee is more than the limit set.
I Don’t Want To Play Any Tournaments

If you are pre-registered for any real money tournaments that are higher than the Buy-in limit opted for,you will be unregistered from the same and the amount will be credited back to your Deposit wallet.
Running tournaments that you are registered for remain unaffected by these set limits.

If you win a free ticket from any satellite tourney and its related final tournament Buy-in is more than the limit set by you, we will restrict you from joining that tournament. As per company policy the value of the satellite ticket will be credited back in form on Instant Bonus to your wallet.
